{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we could go home early, and we did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, this was about 1931 and 1932.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In 1933, when the Nazis came to power, this started to change, because my classmates, who were my little friends, and we visited each other and played together and did our homework together, what have you, must have picked up new vibrations at home, because suddenly they called us dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They called us other names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would not play with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would not invite us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some of their parents would telephone my parents and say I hope you understand, but if my son plays with your son and his other friends will, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They made excuses, but it didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was not an official policy of the school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The teachers were very fair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They never-- this was never permitted in class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was never any reference in class to anything like that, unless the public schools where the anti-Semitism had become suddenly very rampant.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I stayed in that school until there came a point when the government, by this time the National Socialists, the Nazis, decreed that all Jewish children in Germany had to go to special schools-- Jewish schools-- and the consistory of Berlin-- by consistory, I mean the organization of-- to which of the various congregations.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a union of all the synagogues and all the congregations, be they reform or orthodox, which worked together for social relief and what have you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This consistory founded a number of elementary schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were five or six of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I went to number four.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was a regular elementary school, staffed by Jewish teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All the children were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was about 19-- oh, I would say 35 probably.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
